Package: GLEAM
Type: Package
Title: Gene-Set and Cell-State Exploration Across Space and Time in R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Xinjie", "Wu", email = "james@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Xinjie Wu [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Xinjie Wu <james@example.com>
Description: Provides matrix-native signature and cell-state analysis workflows
    across single-cell and spatial transcriptomics. It supports Seurat v4/v5
    compatibility, trajectory-aware mapping, pseudobulk comparisons, and
    publication-friendly visualization with optional ecosystem integrations.
